<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Писателски бележник портфолио </title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,400;0,9..144,600;1,9..144,500&family=Lora:ital,wght@0,400;0,500;1,400&family=Space+Mono:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --parchment: #e8dcc4;
    --parchment-light: #f4ecd8;
    --ink: #2b241c;
    --leather: #7a4a2b;
    --gold: #a6772c;
    --gold-light: #c69a4e;
    --ink-blue: #1f3a5f;
    --ink-blue-dark: #14283f;
    --ink-blue-light: #6f8fb3;
  }

  * { box-sizing: border-box; }

  body {
    margin: 0;
    background: var(--parchment);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-family: 'Lora', serif;
    line-height: 1.65;
    background-image:
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 30%, rgba(122,74,43,0.04) 0%, transparent 40%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 70%, rgba(38,69,58,0.04) 0%, transparent 40%);
  }

  /* СИН ХЕДЪР — вид на мастилено-синя корица с позлатен обков */
  header {
    background: var(--ink-blue);
    background-image: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--ink-blue) 0%, var(--ink-blue-dark) 100%);
    color: var(--parchment-light);
    padding: 4.5rem 1.5rem 3.5rem;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    border-bottom: 6px double var(--gold-light);
  }

  header::before {
    content: "❦";
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  h1.site-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 3.6rem);
    margin: 0;
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .site-tagline {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold-light);
    margin-top: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* MAIN — непроменено спрямо оригиналния "index" дизайн */
  main {
    max-width: 880px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  .shelf-label {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--ink-blue);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink-blue);
    padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.2rem;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
  }

  .cards {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  .card {
    background: var(--parchment-light);
    border: 1px solid rgba(43,36,28,0.15);
    border-radius: 2px;
    padding: 1.9rem 2rem 1.6rem;
    position: relative;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(43,36,28,0.05), 0 8px 18px -12px rgba(43,36,28,0.25);
    transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  }

  .card::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 50%, var(--parchment) 50%);
    box-shadow: -2px 2px 3px -1px rgba(43,36,28,0.25);
  }

  .card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 1px 0 rgba(43,36,28,0.05), 0 14px 24px -12px rgba(43,36,28,0.35);
  }

  .card-date {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--ink-blue);
    border: 1px solid var(--ink-blue);
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.15rem 0.55rem;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transform: rotate(-1.5deg);
    margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
  }

  .card-title {
    font-family: 'Fraunces', serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    color: var(--ink-blue-dark);
  }

  .card-excerpt {
    margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    color: #4a4136;
  }

  .card-link {
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }

  .card-link:hover { color: var(--leather); border-color: var(--leather); }

  footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2.2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    font-family: 'Space Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    color: var(--ink-blue);
    opacity: 0.85;
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    header { padding: 3.2rem 1.2rem 2.6rem; }
    .card { padding: 1.5rem 1.4rem 1.3rem; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <h1 class="site-title">Писателски бележник</h1>
  <div class="site-tagline">разкази · есета · бележки за писане</div>
</header>

<main>
  <div class="shelf-label">
    <span>Последни публикации</span>
    <span>№ картотека</span>
  </div>

  <div class="cards">

    <article class="card">
      <span class="card-date">19.07.2026</span>
      <h2 class="card-title">Заглавие на разказа</h2>
      <p class="card-excerpt">Тук слагаш кратко въведение или първите изречения от текста — колкото да привлечеш читателя да кликне и да продължи.</p>
      <a class="card-link" href="razkaz-1.md">Прочети →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="card">
      <span class="card-date">05.07.2026</span>
      <h2 class="card-title">Второ заглавие</h2>
      <p class="card-excerpt">Кратко описание на втория текст — може да е първият абзац или обобщение в едно изречение.</p>
      <a class="card-link" href="razkaz-2.md">Прочети →</a>
    </article>

  </div>
</main>

<footer>
  © 2026 · всички права запазени
</footer>

</body>
</html>
